ng cartoon character appears briefly against a grey static-like background, then the final red ordering screen appears. It shows the Sega Channel mascot in yellow behind white text: “To order call InterMedia 247-2183” and “Only $11.95/month.” Fine-print copyright and trademark text runs along the bottom.",
